title: [Vornavian Coast, Foggy Valley]
description: Many fallen trees nearly block the path here, slowing progress to a crawl.  The roots of the fallen trees stand tall above the fog off the path to either side.  Despite the felled trees, no moonlight penetrates this place.  A hill to the east looks to be climbable.
